Adam Lamberg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adam_Lamberg 0 Adam Matthew Lamberg (born September 14, 1984) is a former American actor, best known for his portrayal of David "Gordo" Gordon in the Disney Channel series Lizzie McGuire from 2001 through 2004. Lamberg was born in New York City, the son of Suzanne, a retired public high school dance teacher, and Marc Lamberg. His father is Jewish and his mother is French Canadian; Lamberg considers himself to be a "cultural Jew".
